    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those prioritizing utility over aesthetics. The exterior shows noticeable wear, including some scratches and minor dings consistent with its age, and the interior has some staining and visible use on the upholstery. Mechanically, it starts and drives well, though it lacks the smoothness of a newer model and may require routine maintenance soon. It is a solid, honest workhorse for anyone needing dependable transportation at an affordable price point.",
