    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been clearly well-cared for over the years. It offers a smooth, reliable ride and looks great both inside and out, showing only the expected signs of light use for its age. It\u2019s a wonderful opportunity for anyone looking for a dependable, high-quality car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today!",
