    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. It starts reliably and the engine runs smoothly, though potential buyers should expect some noticeable cosmetic wear, including minor scratches on the exterior and some staining on the interior upholstery. Mechanically, it is sound for its age, but it may require routine maintenance soon to keep it in peak operating condition. It is a solid, no-frills choice for someone looking for a car that gets the job done without the premium price of a newer model.",
      "price": 21500.0,
